## Permissions

Datasets not listed here keep whatever permissions are set by hand on the
NAS -- Pulumi doesn't manage them. `Mode` follows `ls -l` notation
(owner/group/other, `r`/`w`/`x` or `-`).

### Identities

| Username | UID | GID | SMB |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
{{#each identities}}
| `{{username}}` | {{uid}} | {{gid}} | {{#if smb}}yes{{else}}no{{/if}} |
{{/each}}

