| Dataset | Owner | Group | Mode | ACL type |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
{{#each acls}}
| `{{path}}` | `{{owner}}` | `{{group}}` | `{{mode}}` | {{acltype}} |
{{/each}}

